headline: RWE to Harness AI-driven Weather Modelling With HPE Private Cloud AI
summary: LONDON, November 21, 2024--Hewlett Packard Enterprise (HPE) today announced that RWE, a leading company in the field of renewable energy, has selected HPE Private Cloud AI to unlock new intelligence from weather data. Researchers at RWE’s Artificial Intelligence (AI) Research Laboratory will utilize the AI-optimized, turnkey private cloud to evaluate, fine tune and inference weather models, harnessing cutting-edge AI to enhance operational decision-making and their global renewable energy leader
